  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/kobean/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u46084242-13.jpg" class="pil" alt="Shengdi" /></a></div>
